    {
      "card": {
        "bgColor": "var(--gray-3)",
        "label": "Lesson 4 • Talking about manufacturing",
        "descriptions": [
          {
            "description": [
              {
                "text": "Mike and Dan work for Swift Shoes, a manufacturer of sneakers. Mike is in charge of manufacturing. Dan is trying to push Mike to get some new shoes ready quickly."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Dan: "
            },
            {
              "text": "We’ve decided to launch our new spring shoe on April 20th."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Mike: "
            },
            {
              "text": "We’re still trying to "
            },
            {
              "markedText": "work out the kinks"
            },
            {
              "text": " in our manufacturing process. Our factory in China is having trouble with the soles."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Dan: "
            },
            {
              "text": "I know that, Mike. But you’ve still got three months. It should be plenty of time."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Mike: "
            },
            {
              "text": "It could take another six months to "
            },
            {
              "markedText": "fine-tune"
            },
            {
              "text": " our manufacturing process."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Dan: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Well, we don’t have that much time. "
            },
            {
              "markedText": "No ifs, ands, or buts"
            },
            {
              "text": ", we need to launch on April 20th."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Mike: "
            },
            {
              "markedText": "Just for the record"
            },
            {
              "text": ", I think we’re "
            },
            {
              "markedText": "cutting it a little close"
            },
            {
              "text": ". I recommend we launch on July 20th instead."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Dan: "
            },
            {
              "text": "We can’t. We’ve already decided on the "
            },
            {
              "markedText": "tagline"
            },
            {
              "text": ": “Spring into spring with Swift’s new spring shoe.”"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Mike: "
            },
            {
              "text": "It’s time for a "
            },
            {
              "markedText": "reality check"
            },
            {
              "text": ". I’m telling you we might not be ready by April 20th, and you’re telling me we have to be because of a tagline?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Dan: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Mike, now’s the time to "
            },
            {
              "markedText": "step up to the plate"
            },
            {
              "text": " and "
            },
            {
              "markedText": "get the job done"
            },
            {
              "text": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Mike: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Well, I’m going to be "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"working down to the wire."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Dan: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Just "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"do whatever it takes"
            },
            {
              "text":	". Just make sure we’ve got a million pairs of shoes in inventory by the April 20th deadline."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Mike: "
            },
            {
              "text": "I’m going to have to run the factories "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	" 24/7"
            },
            {
              "text":	". That’s going to be a lot of overtime pay."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Dan: "
            },
            {
              "markedText": "At the end of the day"
            },
            {
              "text":	", a little extra expense doesn’t matter. We just want those shoes ready by April 20th."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
